le=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HALLOWEENBOY-COMP-SOLICIT-TEMP-WEB-e1779209418669.jpg?fit=768%2C445&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HALLOWEENBOY-COMP-SOLICIT-TEMP-WEB-e1779209418669.jpg?fit=768%2C445&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HALLOWEENBOY-COMP-SOLICIT-TEMP-WEB-e1779209418669.jpg?fit=768%2C445&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<a href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/05/19/dave-bakers-halloween-boy-resurrects-pulp-adventure-comics.html\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Dave Baker&#039;s &quot;Halloween Boy&quot; resurrects pulp adventure comics\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image\" height=\"445\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/boingboing.net/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/HALLOWEENBOY-COMP-SOLICIT-TEMP-WEB-e1779209418669.jpg?fit=768%2C445&amp;quality=60&amp;ssl=1\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 5px;\" width=\"768\" /></a><p><a href=\"https://www.heydavebaker.com/\" id=\"https://www.heydavebaker.com/\" type=\"link\">Dave Baker</a>'s <em>Halloween Boy Vol. 1: Last of the Halloween Boys</em> is a super-fun and clever mash-up of old-school pulp adventure comics, underground comix, and postmodern ennui, all brewed together into a single, satisfying draught. <a href=\"https://onipress.com/\" id=\"https://onipress.com/\" type=\"link\">Oni Pres</a>s is collecting the first five oversized issues of Baker's self-published underground into a hardcover edition arriving May 26, 2026. &#8212; <a class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://boingboing.net/2026/05/19/dave-bakers-halloween-boy-resurrects-pulp-adventure-comics.html\">Read the rest </a></p>\n<p>The post